ái. Với quyết tâm của mình, Lôi Kiên đã trở thành cố vấn cho liên đoàn quyền anh, từ đó gặp gỡ và nảy sinh mối quan hệ mập mờ với Ngạo Sơn.</p>","tmdb_id":139112,"cast":["Lê Diệu Tường","Elaine Yiu","Trương Chấn Lãng","Hugo Wong","Thái Khiết","Winki Lai","Chu Mẫn Hãn","Đàm Tuấn Ngạn"],"director":[],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"139112","season":1,"vote_average":7,"vote_count":1},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Lê Diệu Tường","name_vi":"Lê Diệu Tường","name_original":"Wayne Lai Yiu-Cheung","tmdb_id":123654,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qm3knPxzkZPgq2SVo1ZTru7MkIM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/123654"},{"name":"Elaine Yiu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Elaine Yiu","tmdb_id":1234807,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/CV05R5HbE4MnpeWeE5HAFaV2bG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1234807"},{"name":"Trương Chấn Lãng","name_vi":"Trương Chấn Lãng","name_original":"Owen Cheung","tmdb_id":1613713,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xwg4ha6y8nk6P9V8NHQLV0iKRmL.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1613713"},{"name":"Hugo Wong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Hugo Wong","tmdb_id":2370809,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gAIsL0FeiMSS1Ien1OaVYYassUv.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2370809"},{"name":"Thái Khiết","name_vi":"Thái Khiết","name_original":"Jacky Cai","tmdb_id":1450374,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rt0aCtGoKIiCObfdV9JhP6nRiUE.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1450374"},{"name":"Winki Lai","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Winki Lai","tmdb_id":2064586,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bhg2Q2fS3sV9nkBpsyhLC2aq4ym.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2064586"},{"name":"Chu Mẫn Hãn","name_vi":"Chu Mẫn Hãn","name_original":"Brian Chu","tmdb_id":2705751,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lZzBMzKAN8s9KNY2fXJ21xDgNeu.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2705751"},{"name":"Đàm Tuấn Ngạn","name_vi":"Đ